data.description: Stunning home with primary bedroom suite on main level and views of tranquil wooded area in back yard. Great entertainment deck with retractable awning plus concrete patio below. Travertine flooring on main level, custom kitchen and bathrooms with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, formal dining room and vaulted ceilings with skylights for natural light. Newer interior and exterior paint are just a few of the outstanding features this home as to offer.  New roof and skylights in 2021 along with camera and security system installed.  Come home to a great neighborhood located in one of Wilsonville's finest areas.
